<emphasis id="460D1AE544CB6EAC1DC43EFA2680C0F0" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">B. Balansa 801</emphasis>
(lectotypes, designated here: G-BOIS! [G00544628]; isolectotypes: G! [G00378630, G00378631], K! [K000728449], JE! [JE00016142, JE00016143], L [L.1713650], WAG! [WAG0004032])
</paragraph>
